>>16048357
First off, you have to establish how slavery works in your world. Is it a major industry, openly practiced with large markets and proper traders? Or is it a backwater kind of thing only practiced on the edges of civilization? Maybe even an illegal practice only found underground.
If it is legal, what is the scale? What laws surround it? Limits of what a master can do? One of the big things here is determining who the slaves are. Is it based on species? Debts? Being captured in battle?
What are the industries that generally use slaves? Manual labor? Skilled labor? Manufacturing? Agriculture? Domestic services? I'd suggest the last one for your purposes of writing a fic.

All these things determine what kind of a story you want to tell.
